# 📒 Contact Book

A simple Contact Book application built using Python. This project allows users to add, view, search, and delete contacts using a menu-driven interface.

## 🚀 Features

- Add New Contacts
- View All Contacts
- Search Contact by Name
- Delete Contact
- Exit Application

## 📌 Concepts Used

- Dictionaries
- Loops (`while`, `for`)
- Conditional Statements (`if-elif-else`)
- User Input
- Dictionary Methods (`pop`)
- Menu-Driven Programming

## 🎯 Learning Outcomes

Through this project, I learned:

- How to use Python Dictionaries
- How to store data as Key-Value pairs
- How to search data in a dictionary
- How to delete dictionary entries
- How to create menu-driven applications
- How to work with loops and conditions



## ⭐ Project Status

Completed as an Intermediate Python Project.
